---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Massage Services | Ahhh A Massage — McMurray, PA"
  description="Relaxation massage, medical massage, table massage, and chair massage. Holistic therapeutic massage tailored to your needs."
>
  <section class="bg-sage-pale py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="line-sage mb-4"></div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-charcoal leading-tight mb-6">Our Services</h1>
        <p class="text-earth text-lg leading-relaxed">Your therapeutic massage experience should be as unique as you. Designed to relieve and heal the root causes of stress, tension, and chronic pain.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain & Stress -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center reveal">
        <div>
          <p class="text-lavender uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4">Pain & Tension</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-charcoal mb-6">When Pain Takes Over</h2>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Most people seek massage as a last resort for pain and stress. They try taking pills and other medical treatments that haven't worked. With over 20 years of experience as a massage therapist and decades as a registered nurse, Margie can recommend treatments and therapies to improve your overall well-being, along with massage.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-sage-pale flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-earth text-sm"><strong class="text-charcoal">Stress:</strong> Poor posture, constant mental pressure, and sedentary lifestyles leave your muscles aching. Massage therapy and aromatherapy can help you relax and drain the exhaustion.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-sage-pale flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-earth text-sm"><strong class="text-charcoal">Pain:</strong> Arthritis, fibromyalgia, muscle spasms, carpal tunnel, post-surgery, repetitive movement injuries, and chemotherapy — Margie knows exactly how to help.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-8 text-sage-dark font-medium">Call for a free consultation: <a href="tel:4128778569" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-sage">(412) 877-8569</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/studio.jpg" alt="Inside the massage studio" class="rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Types -->
  <section class="bg-stone py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 reveal">
        <div class="line-sage mx-auto mb-4"></div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-charcoal">Massage Types</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-sage-pale reveal">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-sage-pale flex items-center justify-center text-sage">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-4 mb-3">Relaxation Massage</h3>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">This relaxing massage is intended to help you release tension in the body and relax, lowering stress levels, improving circulation, and provide the therapeutic touch you're missing in your life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-sage-pale reveal">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-lavender-pale flex items-center justify-center text-lavender">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-4 mb-3">Medical Massage</h3>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">Sometimes you need more than stress relief and relaxation. Medical massage can help you manage pain, reduce inflammation, relieve nerve compression, and even improve digestion.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-sage-pale reveal">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-sage-pale flex items-center justify-center text-sage">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-4 mb-3">Table Massage</h3>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">The table massage is a full-body massage. You can schedule a session for 60 or 90 minutes. A nurturing experience, meant to work out all the kinks and stress of your day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-sage-pale reveal">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-sage-pale flex items-center justify-center text-sage">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-4 mb-3">Chair Massage</h3>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">If you're short on time, a chair massage is a convenient treatment to squeeze into a lunch break. No clothing needs to be removed. Return to work feeling more alert and focused.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gift Certificates & Intake -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 reveal">
        <div class="bg-lavender-pale rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-medium text-charcoal mb-3">Gift Certificates</h3>
          <p class="text-earth text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Give the gift of healing and relaxation to someone you love.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline text-sm">Inquire About Gift Certificates</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-sage-pale rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-medium text-charcoal mb-3">Patient Intake Form</h3>
          <p class="text-earth text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Please download and complete the intake form before your first visit. Be honest and thorough — Margie will ask additional questions to understand the big picture.</p>
          <a href="https://irp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/6097f8c0/files/uploaded/Intake%20Form%20-%20New.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-sage text-sm">
            Download Intake Form
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-sage-dark py-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-light text-white mb-4">Ready to Begin?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 mb-8">Call for a free consultation.</p>
      <a href="tel:4128778569" class="btn bg-white text-sage-dark border-2 border-white hover:bg-transparent hover:text-white">Call Margie — (412) 877-8569</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
